      "score": 1754,
      "text": "<a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discord.com&#x2F;press-releases&#x2F;discord-launches-teen-by-default-settings-globally\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discord.com&#x2F;press-releases&#x2F;discord-launches-teen-by-...</a><p><a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discord.com&#x2F;safety&#x2F;how-discord-is-building-safer-experiences-for-teens\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;discord.com&#x2F;safety&#x2F;how-discord-is-building-safer-exp...</a>",
